# How to Participate  

- “Follow” [@thedeveco](https://x.com/thedeveco) on X (must be able to Direct Message winner) 
- “Like” the entry Tweet 
- “Comment” and “Tag” someone on the entry Tweet
- (Optional) In your "Comment", tell [@](https://X.com/thedeveco) something you enjoyed about @Hackaday Remoticon 2020 virtual event. 
- “Retweet” the entry Tweet

## Useful resources: 

- Link to @thedeveco X channel: https://x.com/thedeveco 
- Link to the devEco YouTube channel: https://www.youtube.com/@thedeveco
- Link to the devEco GitHub: https://github.com/deveco

