This competition is provided and administered by the devEco community on behalf of itself and its participating partners and partner communities. 

### Eligibility  

The competition is only open to participants 18 years or older, who are residents of the United States of America ONLY. No Purchase Necessary. No employee of devEco is eligible to participate in the competition. 

### Entry period and criteria  

Entries may be submitted at https://X.com/thedeveco (via interaction with entry Tweet) from [DATE] at [TIME] and you must submit your entry by [TIME] [DATE]. All entries (Like, Follow, Comments, and Retweet with quote to entry Tweet) must be written in English.  

